Dialogue: 100,0:00:04.38,0:00:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,05, interceptează inamicul.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.21,0:00:10.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recepționat. Voi prioritiza salvarea civililor.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.46,0:00:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se presupunea că sunt salvatorul lor, și totuși...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.54,0:00:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}nu am fost întâmpinat cu urale, ci cu niște ochi plini de frică și așteptări imense.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.25,0:00:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar nu-mi pasă.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.63,0:00:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voi proteja umanitatea.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.46,0:00:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doar pentru asta exist.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.08,0:00:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Voi proteja lumea.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.75,0:00:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doar asta se vrea de la mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.42,0:00:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doar pentru asta trăiesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.54,0:00:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Un coșmar...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și ce mai coșmar.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.96,0:02:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar acum știu că toată ziua va fi una nasoală...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.83,0:02:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E venită direct de la regina Echidna: „Cavalerul Onixului Negru trebuie să-mi raporteze imediat.”
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce? Și-a dat cumva seama cine sunt?!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce vei face acum?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.67,0:02:54.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și Lily a fost cât pe ce să-mi dezvălui adevărata identitate, dar am reușit s-o opresc.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.38,0:03:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încă nu ai fost să i te prezinți. Poate că e supărată din cauza asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.67,0:03:02.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O, așa e. Nu am făcut asta încă...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:02.88,0:03:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar, vezi tu...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.00,0:03:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-am spus că treburile noastre merg bine datorită ajutorului lui Onyx...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.79,0:03:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cel mai probabil de asta vrea să mă vadă, proasto!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.75,0:03:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Proastă?! C-Ce altceva ar fi trebuit să-i spun?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.88,0:03:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar Echidna nu a primit din întâmplare titlul de Regină Demon.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.46,0:03:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înarmată cu mult iubita ei sabie, Tilving, poate lupta de la egal la egal cu Edvard
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.08,0:03:29.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și e la fel de bună la vrăji precum Shutina. E înfricoșător de puternică.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.83,0:03:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indiferent ce trucuri aș folosi, ar putea să vadă dincolo de deghizarea mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.75,0:03:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,În acest caz, ar trebui să te grăbești la ea.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.54,0:03:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și dacă-și dă seama cine ești, cheamă-mă fără ezitare.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.25,0:03:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Voi fi în regulă. Mă voi descurca pe cont propriu.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.71,0:03:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doar să te prefaci că nu ai știut nimic.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.58,0:03:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și acum, ce scuză îi voi oferi lui Echidna?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.75,0:03:59.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aici Cavalerul Negru, Onyx.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.67,0:04:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am venit la chemarea Înălțimii Voastre.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.71,0:04:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Intră.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.08,0:04:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bun, ia să vedem ce mi-ai pregătit, Regină Demon, Echidna?!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:07.17,0:04:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă mulțumesc.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci tu ești incredibilul Onyx!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.83,0:04:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am auzit totul despre faptele tale extraordinare de la Shutina!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi cer scuze că te-am chemat aici atât de din scurt.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.33,0:04:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine... Se pare că nu și-a dat seama cine sunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.50,0:04:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ia un loc, te rog.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.54,0:04:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ce? Nu se poate... Cred că-ți bați joc de mine. Cineva să mă scape!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.29,0:04:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunt doar două locuri la acea masă!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.00,0:04:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide să lăsăm formalitățile pentru astăzi
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și să ne bucurăm împreună de o masă bogată și o băutură bună!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.96,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}De fiecare dată când am coșmaruri, știu că ziua următoare va fi una oribilă.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bei și tu, lord Onyx?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, da.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.17,0:04:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să spun, acest lichior e incredibil. \NSă nu mai vorbesc de mâncare.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.21,0:04:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excelent!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.50,0:04:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This looks like your typical after-hours drink\Nwith a strait-laced worker and his chill boss.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.04,0:05:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's anything but.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to get out of here as quickly as humanly possible,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.33,0:05:08.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I'm terrified she'll find out\Nwho I am in the midst of all this.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.54,0:05:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci, Onyx...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.79,0:05:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Da?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.00,0:05:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to wear that helm for much longer?\NWould you please take it off?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:15.50,0:05:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I must insist. It would be rude to show\Nmy bare face before you, Your Highness...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, I told you to dispense with formalities.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.83,0:05:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și mi-ar plăcea să-ți văd fața în timp ce discutăm!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.25,0:05:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, ei bine...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.92,0:05:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și acum, să vedem ce față barbară se ascunde în spatele acelei măști!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.83,0:05:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nu!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și uite-o!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stai o secundă...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu am avut timp încât să-mi schimb fața prea mult!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.67,0:05:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-E ceva în neregulă?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi place expresia ta devotată!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simt o putere imensă ce se ascunde în spatele chipului tău blând!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E mare păcat să-l ascunzi în spatele unei măști!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.92,0:06:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fost cât pe ce! Ce noroc pe mine că s-a îmbătat...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.33,0:06:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, nu te abține.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.58,0:06:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stuff yourself until you burst, by all means!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.88,0:06:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beau singur cu șefa mea și dacă va afla cine sunt, s-a zis cu mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cum ar trebui să savurez alcoolul în această situație?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.71,0:06:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mâncarea și băutura sunt divine! Aceasta este raiul pe pământ!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.08,0:06:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trebuie să scap cât mai repede cu putință din acest rai.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dar trebuie să acționez inteligent și calm.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:34.25,0:06:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înălțimea Voastră, paharul vi s-a golit.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Permiteți-mi să vi-l umplu.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, mersi! Cât de atent din partea ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă-mi permiteți...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:45.04,0:06:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me give you a couple tips about how\Nto make business parties a little easier.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.21,0:06:53.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tip #1: The moment your boss' glass is empty, fill it up.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, have some more.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.08,0:06:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.13,0:07:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can take a break from the conversation\Nwhile filling their cup,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and they'll think you're perceptive and cosiderate.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, have another!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.83,0:07:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.50,0:07:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's not the only thing I'm after.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.75,0:07:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, my goal is simple: get her dead drunk!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I'm focused on!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.42,0:07:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, you're thirsty! Come, have another!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:14.75,0:07:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.08,0:07:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C'mon, drink! Drink 'til you're sloshed!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.96,0:07:25.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then you can put an end to this horrible event!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă simțiți bine, Înălțimea Voastră?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.50,0:07:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poate ați băut un pic cam mult?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.38,0:07:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cred că ar fi mai bine să...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.58,0:07:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da, ai dreptate...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum că ne-am încălzit, \Nsă bem direct din sticlă!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haide, bea, Onyx!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.88,0:07:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu fi timid! Dă-o pe gât!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though this strategy won't work against\Nheavyweights, so keep THAT in mind.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've been able\Nto enjoy a relaxing spot of tea.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.13,0:08:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să-i mulțumesc și lui Leo pentru asta...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.17,0:08:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă întreb cum merge întâlnirea sa.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sper că totul e în regulă.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.25,0:08:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poate ar trebui să merg și să-i verific...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.63,0:08:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai bine nu, dacă spun ceva greșit și înrăutățesc lucrurile?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And why am I getting all worked up over that hero?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți faci griji pentru Leo?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.83,0:08:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uite raportul meu!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.50,0:08:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Lily?! N-Nu ai auzit nimic, nu-i așa?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.38,0:08:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cred că ți s-a părut! Da, nu am spus absolut nimic!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:38.71,0:08:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poftim? Ce tot spui acolo?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.71,0:08:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nu am putut s-o dobor cu alcoolul, \Ndar nu voi renunța acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:45.88,0:08:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mai am un as în mânecă...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Din nefericire, va dura \Nceva ca să-și facă efectul.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just need to segue into it..
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.79,0:08:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must say, this food is scrumptious.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.96,0:09:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the sausage you're now eating,\NYour Highness. It's simply to die for.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.33,0:09:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've an eye for quality, then?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something in this sausage\Nthat makes it truly fantastic.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tip #2 for making drinking parties less of a headache:
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.46,0:09:17.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People are fond of those who show\Nan active interest in them and their tastes.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:17.50,0:09:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when you're eating and drinking together,\Nyou have all the fodder you need.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.75,0:09:27.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sausage is made with spices from Largo.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.42,0:09:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The minced pepper inside gives it\Nsuch a pleasant color, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Largo, you say?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been hurting for resources so much lately,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.83,0:09:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I rarely had time to enjoy such extravagant meals.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.29,0:09:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But thanks to Lily's efforts, things are slowly improving.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I always knew she could handle the task.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.83,0:09:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at that innocent smile.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:49.13,0:09:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She looks like a normal girl when she smiles like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:51.75,0:09:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have to give credit to the chefs\Nwho prepared the food so expertly.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should know that those sausages\Nwere made by yours truly.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:00.00,0:10:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cooks down at the Demon Rat Davern,\Nthe castle dining hall, made absolute slop,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I shared some key recipes and\Ntrained them on how to make them.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:07.63,0:10:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which leads to Tip #3: if there's food,\Nlearn as much as you can about it beforehand!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.25,0:10:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the food topic can lead to any manner\Nof conversation. It's an excellent segue.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.75,0:10:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After what Shutina told me, I was curious\Nabout the kind of man you were...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.96,0:10:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But not only are you great at your job,\Nyou're also a culinary expert!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're quite the man, Lord Onyx!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.83,0:10:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hardly, Your Highness. My talents\Nand knowledge are all quite modest.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.83,0:10:32.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's just one thing I have to ask.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.75,0:10:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to always wear that helm of yours.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.21,0:10:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know we touched on this before,\Nbut could you explain why?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.83,0:10:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, you see...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Time for Tip #4!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.13,0:10:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only time a powerless newbie\Ncan sell themselves to the boss
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is when the boss asks them questions!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:49.88,0:10:54.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your answer can drastically change the flow\Nof the outing, or your workload the next day!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.17,0:10:58.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You see, I've been cursed by the goddess Tiana.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.25,0:11:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time I'm allowed to show my face\Nto others is gravely limited.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.67,0:11:05.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As such, I must spend most\Nof my time encased in armor.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.00,0:11:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goodness... And you've been without your helm\Nthis whole time. Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.08,0:11:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be frank, I may be cutting it close.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.42,0:11:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad to take that risk if it means\Na chance to spend time with Your Highness.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:18.54,0:11:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop. You're quite the talker, aren't you!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is how you get out of a drinking excursion early.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:25.13,0:11:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mention you have a clear-cut time limit,\Nand you can escape any horrific situation!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.92,0:11:34.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now Echidna knows I'm working with limited time here...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a great day today has been!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A toast to the friendship between\NBlack Knight Onyx and Demon Queen Echidna!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.71,0:11:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us drink and talk the night away!\NDown that bottle, now!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:48.25,0:11:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drink the night away? Goodness, I'd be delighted...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.63,0:11:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you want Leo to have to go away?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.88,0:11:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.67,0:12:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?! Do you?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.58,0:12:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-well no, but...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.42,0:12:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,General Shutina! Are you there?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.25,0:12:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dianette? You sound distressed. Is everything all right?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have an extremely urgent message for you!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.58,0:12:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a few hours since\Nthis drinking party from hell began,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.50,0:12:26.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and while she hasn't figured out who I am yet,\NI still want to get the hell out of here...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.67,0:12:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lord Onyx, I'm deeply grateful for all you've done.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.13,0:12:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only did you lessen Shutina's workload\Nmere moments after you arrived,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.67,0:12:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you've also been keeping a watchful eye on Lily.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:37.75,0:12:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your efforts have been of great help to us all.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.38,0:12:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I arranged this feast to thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Echidna...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.88,0:12:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sunteți mult prea amabilă, \NÎnălțimea Voastră.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.21,0:12:53.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human or demon, we gladly welcome all\Nwho have skills to donate to our cause.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so very glad we have you among\Nour ranks in the Demon Army!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.42,0:12:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, then...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What of that hero, Leo?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.00,0:13:06.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard he wanted to join. Would you welcome him, to?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hero?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one exception! I don't want him here!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:12.25,0:13:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That twisted man, that social reject!\NHe's the last person I'd want in my army!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:17.29,0:13:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we were foolish enough to let him join,\Nhe'd destroy us from the inside out!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.42,0:13:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right here. Literally right in front of you.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.58,0:13:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's already made things\NWAY better for your organization.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.38,0:13:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't care if he does a thousand,\Nor ten thousand hands' worth of work!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.21,0:13:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for that blasted hero,\NI would've had the Philosopher's Stone by now!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.13,0:13:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So THAT was what she was after.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.46,0:13:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all because of him! All his fault!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.00,0:13:44.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Damn it! Damn it all!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.21,0:13:46.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's leave her to stew and talk\Nabout this Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.08,0:13:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Philosopher's Stone is a treasure\Nheld in the holy city of Renailles.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.79,0:13:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's said that the first saint-king\Ndug it up over 3,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:57.71,0:14:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then used its power to found the Capital proper.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.25,0:14:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors say the Philosopher's Stone turned\Nthe wastelands around the city to green fields,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.17,0:14:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,protected the city's people from plague,\Nand could even make someone immortal.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.92,0:14:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most of these rumors are bogus, of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.83,0:14:21.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do I know? Because I've used it before.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.17,0:14:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Stone in the Capital isn't the one I used, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.46,0:14:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Philosopher's Stone wouldn't\Ngive someone super powers or anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not a magic power-up or cure-all.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you looked up "the worst" in the dictionary,\Nhis name would be there in the definition!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}And he'd be in the definition for MORON, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, she's STILL going?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much trash does she have to talk about me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how close we were?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.00,0:14:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were so deep into Renailles that\Nwe could see the Stone's sacred hall,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.13,0:14:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and if we'd gotten the Stone,\Nwe could've accomplished all we came for!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.71,0:14:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.17,0:14:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the reason you haven't retreated,\Ndespite losing so many men,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.96,0:15:03.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is because you're not after conquest,\Nbut the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.79,0:15:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.50,0:15:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was far too aggressive with that war.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.50,0:15:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't have to fight all of humanity\Njust to obtain the Philosopher's Stone.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not deceive them, or steal it?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or work with them.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:20.25,0:15:24.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a children's tale about human\Nand demonkind joining forces, isn't there?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Eibrad, the Joiner of Hands", I believe?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:27.29,0:15:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's an old human story.\NI heard it myself from a succubus storyteller.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.08,0:15:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It tells of an oddball imp who travels to the human world
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.75,0:15:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and builds a city where humans\Nand demons live in harmony.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.71,0:15:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it pales in comparison to our reality.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.67,0:15:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Human and demon are destined\Nto be at odds with one another.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.63,0:15:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The story is just that: a story.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.29,0:15:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which only makes me even\Nmore curious about your goals.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.33,0:15:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you plan to do with the Philosopher's Stone?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.08,0:16:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ever since her defeat, I've been dying to know...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:03.92,0:16:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After being beaten into submission,\Nlosing most of her army and territory,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why hasn't she returned to the Demon World?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:13.58,0:16:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she was after something silly\Nlike immortality or riches,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she would've lost motivation and left long ago.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.83,0:16:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why does she still persist? Why is she still here\Nin this castle, rebuilding her army?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.63,0:16:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:35.42,0:16:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow... What an incredible view.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.00,0:16:41.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it's the most beautiful in this light.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been to the Demon World?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have not.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:47.13,0:16:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Demon World, our home, is a grand, vast wasteland.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.33,0:17:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has no sun, no vegetation. The air is heavy,\Nand the water is muddy and impure.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Demon clans fight one another over\Nthe little resources that remain,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.63,0:17:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,staining the wasteland with blood.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A demonic world indeed.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am sick of it.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.04,0:17:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish to bring order to my world of chaos.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:17.08,0:17:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To rid the land of conflict.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:20.00,0:17:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To bathe it in the warm sunlight, to cleanse\Nthe waters to sparkle in that light.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.25,0:17:32.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish for fish to swim in those waters, and\Nfor grasslands and forests to sway in the wind.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.13,0:17:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is why I sought the help of Shutina\Nand other skilled comrades:
Dialogue: 100,0:17:39.38,0:17:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To come to the human world and retrieve\Nthe Philosopher's Stone to reforge the land.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.67,0:17:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This whole time, she's been fighting humanity\Nto better the lives of her people...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised to hear these wishes coming\Nfrom the Demon Queen's lips?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.58,0:18:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I'm accustomed to this reaction.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.25,0:18:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no quarrel with the humans,\Nbut the Philosopher's Stone will be ours.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:12.04,0:18:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they willingly offered it up, then,\Nyou'd accept it without shedding blood?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.04,0:18:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, but even if we explained\Nour good-natured intentions, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The holy Capital is the center of the human realm.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:23.75,0:18:29.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stealing the very thing that holds that\Ncity together would hurt their livelihoods.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's a sacrifice I'm willing to make.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those who cooperate with us, like the dragonfolk\Nand the humans from Lily's home,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.50,0:18:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,will all be given sanctuary in the Demon World,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.96,0:18:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I care not what happens to the other humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:42.50,0:18:45.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't! Not in the slightest!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.58,0:18:49.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, Your Majesty, you've forbidden\Nneedless killing, have you not?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.50,0:18:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is an invasion, but we must\Navoid killing whenever possible!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.08,0:19:01.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that policy is why the war ended\Nwith mercifully low casualties on both sides.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.13,0:19:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look where that got us: defeat. I curse my naivete.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I simply could not fully become the villain.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans may be our enemy,\Nbut they have homes they want to protect, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:15.13,0:19:19.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And friends, and family... Considering that,\NI simply couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:21.33,0:19:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be honest about the Hero Leo...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.88,0:19:27.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't bear him any ill will.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Might I ask why?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:30.58,0:19:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a hero. He exists to protect humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.46,0:19:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't fault him for doing just that:\Nfighting an invader attacking humanity.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.38,0:19:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may have put a stop to my plans,\Nbut he was not wrong to do so.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:47.63,0:19:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fault lay with us, the aggressors in this war.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see her differently now.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:55.13,0:19:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's kind. A loving Queen who cares for her people.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:00.25,0:20:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet she became an evil conquerer\Nto provide for her beloved subjects.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:06.42,0:20:08.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have wondered\Nif she was doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:08.67,0:20:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must have been assailed by anxiety,\Nunspeakable despair, and ever-present worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.67,0:20:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then someone brought\Nabout the greatest despair of all.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:18.71,0:20:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, the Hero Leo.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about you, Onyx?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:25.96,0:20:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you join us?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:29.08,0:20:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did humanity betray you?\NDo you wish to put an end to this world?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:33.46,0:20:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or have you simply come seeking a place to die?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.17,0:20:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wish to hear your motivation.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:42.63,0:20:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.46,0:20:47.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is why I hate going out drinking with colleagues.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.33,0:20:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were shooting the shit, then suddenly\Ngot into a serious topic where I have to be honest.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be easy to lie,
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but she's just opened her heart to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I deceived her further, she'd be even\Nmore upset when I revealed who I was...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:03.75,0:21:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.92,0:21:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't want to lie to her anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:10.08,0:21:14.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not as part of any strategy, but because\NI genuinely want to support her.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:14.79,0:21:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially now that I know\Nshe just wants to save her home.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:18.17,0:21:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:20.29,0:21:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, I suppose I should tell you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Îi voi spune cine sunt.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.63,0:21:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Îmi voi cere scuze că m-am dat altcineva și îi voi spune cât de mult vreau să ajut.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Înălțimea Voastră, eu...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.79,0:21:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.46,0:21:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu, Echidna, eu...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:36.33,0:21:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:39.17,0:21:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, I finally found you....
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.21,0:21:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Generals?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:43.46,0:21:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's real bad! We got a problem!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:46.38,0:21:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Poftim...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.00,0:21:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going on a journey.\NPlease don't come looking for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.29,0:21:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shadowless General Mernes.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:55.21,0:21:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have failed to properly train my troops\Nand will be taking my life to make amends.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:58.92,0:22:00.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Generalul-dragon Edvard.
